Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.76,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:18.44,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要唤出情感之名 则无休无止无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:26.53,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神传来呼唤 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.36,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相随
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.61,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不离不弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:33.20,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无论光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:37.08,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如紧凑相连的拼图零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.33,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:45.59,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:50.26,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}终将指引我们走向所坚信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:57.02,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤诚真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:00.85,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}无虚情假意 非利益所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:05.61,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真实自我
